cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is primarily focused on natural language processing tasks, specifically sequence generation from undirected neural sequence models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a generalized framework for sequence generation, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper uses various neural network architectures, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed approach on a machine translation task, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) as it involves processing visual data.
